{"tid":2310653,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【新股IPO】Airbnb美IPO定價區間44至50美元 集資最多201億","createTime":"2020-12-03T11:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T16:40:52.000Z","uid":62073,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"abb53a745159c87ea8128abac0fc5acb3ee12fbf","tid":2310653,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T11:56:28.000Z","msg":"【新股IPO】Airbnb美IPO定價區間44至50美元 集資最多201億<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【新股IPO】Airbnb美IPO定價區間44至50美元 集資最多201億（第三版）<br />\n 新股IPO 23:33 2020/12/01 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網上短租住宿平台Airbnb（美：ABNB）將於美國上市，據美國證交會更新的招股文件顯示，Airbnb擬發行5191.4萬股A類股，IPO定價為每股44至50美元，集資最多25.95億美元（約201.2億港元）。摩根士丹利及高盛為主要承銷團。Airbnb計劃於今年年底掛牌。<br />\n<br />\n據初步招股書顯示，截至今年9月底止9個月，Airbnb淨虧損擴大3.74億元至6.97億元（約54.3億港元），去年同期為3.23億元。期內，收入為25.2億元，按年下跌32%，去年同期為37億元。<br />\n<br />\n單計今年第三季，公司純利錄2.19億元，按年下跌17.7%；收入按年跌19%至13.4億元。公司於今年首次單季獲得利潤，主要因公司積極削減成本。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n集團今年首季、次季虧損分別為3.4億元及5.75億元。<br />\n<br />\n據知情人士稱，Airbnb目前計劃在12月9日確定IPO發行價，並於次日開始在納斯達克全球精選市場交易。基於26億美元的融資額，Airbnb此次IPO將成為今年美國第四大IPO。"},{"pid":"4cadf2b0f79717d1916c3773736abd88b127943e","tid":2310653,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T12:16:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472bb8fcb4f921c4a3e1bb7b7a236b9f7fa065aa","tid":2310653,"uid":365454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T12:24:15.000Z","msg":"都冇得抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53d0b69928b85adf0e70f44e16ac16127d8aed3","tid":2310653,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T12:31:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3a5a9dbb1fe6ee53a8c8ce287dbf8d487bdb5da","tid":2310653,"uid":82389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:42:37.000Z","msg":"呢隻SH得過？"},{"pid":"c4e5f1b0d7e8872c7fc9c2b4b42de3471bee8bde","tid":2310653,"uid":374818,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:47:16.000Z","msg":"支肺影響咁大<br />\n依家先黎上市....<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3dd8d33d43d84e2e388ae9182662cd969d9a787","tid":2310653,"uid":132898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T15:50:00.000Z","msg":"似入得過。。？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01d38e5637352b06fc26d0e3c53cfd50d1c3a4a6","tid":2310653,"uid":12463,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:35:16.000Z","msg":"邊個有得抽美股"},{"pid":"bb6728495586ab2ad2fc0ce597391f5e11b2515b","tid":2310653,"uid":184932,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-03T16:40:52.000Z","msg":"drop下先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n肺炎抽到都京"}]}